OL,3,CMother publishes moving memoir
OL,4,Cfollowing accident that claimed
OL,5,Cdaughter's life
OL,7,FA woman whose life was devastated by
OL,8,Fthe loss of her daughter in a car
OL,9,Fcrash - and who was paralyzed from the
OL,10,Fchest down in the accident, has
OL,11,Fwritten a book she hopes will help
OL,12,Fothers dealing with disability and
OL,13,Fgrief.
OL,15,FDanielle Elm, 37, was a well-known
OL,16,Ffigure in Swanage in Dorset, long
OL,17,Fbefore the tragedy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
