OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777385513
OL,3,CMother publishes moving memoir
OL,4,Cfollowing accident that claimed
OL,5,Cdaughter's life
OL,7,FA former Carnival Queen and
OL,8,Fentertainment rep, she and her husband
OL,9,FDan had celebrated what they called a
OL,10,F"miracle" pregnancy with their
OL,11,Fdaughter, Darcy, after doctors
OL,12,Finitially told Dani she would never
OL,13,Fconceive.
OL,15,FHowever, their lives were shattered in
OL,16,FOctober 2018 during a family trip to
OL,17,FWales.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
