CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777385513
OL,3,CMother publishes moving memoir
OL,4,Cfollowing accident that claimed
OL,5,Cdaughter's life
OL,7,FThe last image of the family together
OL,8,Fwas captured through the eyes of four-
OL,9,Fyear-old Darcy, who had been playing
OL,10,Fwith her mother's iPad in the back of
OL,11,Fthe car just an hour before the
OL,12,Fcollision.
OL,14,F"Darcy was a beautiful ray of
OL,15,Fsunshine," Dani told ITV Meridian. "I
OL,16,Fmean, she stole the hearts of so many
OL,17,Fpeople locally."
OL,19,FWhile Darcy tragically did not
OL,20,Fsurvive, Dani spent months in a coma
OL,21,Fwith serious brain and spinal injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
