PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777385513
OL,3,CMother publishes moving memoir
OL,4,Cfollowing accident that claimed
OL,5,Cdaughter's life
OL,7,F"I wanted to know if I was going to go
OL,8,Fsurfing again... I wanted to know if I
OL,9,Fwas going to feel like a normal
OL,10,Fwoman," she explained.
OL,12,F"I couldn't find those answers. So now
OL,13,FI have provided that information in
OL,14,Fthe book."
OL,16,FThe result is Our Last Steps.
OL,18,FWhile Dani has no memory of the crash,
OL,19,Fher husband Dan, who is now her full-
OL,20,Ftime carer, remembers everything.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
