PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777385513
OL,3,CMother publishes moving memoir
OL,4,Cfollowing accident that claimed
OL,5,Cdaughter's life
OL,7,FHe has been receiving treatment for
OL,8,FPTSD, including flashbacks and the
OL,9,Femotional toll of the accident.
OL,11,F"I didn't really have anyone else to
OL,12,Ftalk to," Dan said. "It was really
OL,13,Fhard to talk to Dani about what
OL,14,Fhappened with losing Darcy and the
OL,15,Faccident... going through counselling
OL,16,Fwith the PTSD really helped me."
OL,18,FDespite the pain, the couple ensures
OL,19,FDarcy remains the heart of their home.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
