PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777385513
OL,3,CMother publishes moving memoir
OL,4,Cfollowing accident that claimed
OL,5,Cdaughter's life
OL,7,F"She's never been in this house, but
OL,8,Fshe oozes from these walls," Dani
OL,9,Fsaid. "I'm not afraid to see a picture
OL,10,Fof my daughter."
OL,12,FDani is sharing the proceeds of the
OL,13,Fbook between 2Wish - a charity
OL,14,Fsupporting families who have suffered
OL,15,Fthe sudden loss of a child, and
OL,16,FSwanage Carnival.
OL,18,FAs for the future, the couple is
OL,19,Fpreparing for a new chapter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
